text: Unlocked is a 2017 American British French Czech Swiss action thriller movie directed by Michael Apted and starring Noomi Rapace, Orlando Broom, Michael Douglas, John Malkovich, Toni Collette, Tosin Cole, Adelayo Adedayo.
